# LiveChartRenderer - Real-Time Plotting Tool  

LiveChartRenderer converts numeric streams into animated graphs for immediate trend analysis.

## Features:
- Matplotlib-based live graphs  
- Synthetic or custom data streams  
- Pauses and restarts supported  

## Installation & Usage  
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/23_LiveChartRenderer.git  
cd 23_LiveChartRenderer  
python visualize.py  
